caption.p: Gas chromatogram of the leaf essential oil of Commiphora gileadensis. The major components are indicated: a, α-thujene; b, α-pinene; c, camphene; d, sabinene; e, β-pinene; f, myrcene; g, p-cymene; h, limonene; i, γ-terpinene; j, terpinolene; k, cis-p-menth-2-en-1-ol; l, terpinen-4-ol; m, bornyl acetate; n, ( E)-caryophyllene; o, germacrene D; p, 1,10-di- epi-cubenol.
